@startuml
title Decorator - Ejemplo 2 - solucion para flujos de datos
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class BufferedStream {
    +read(): String
  }
  interface DataStream <<interfaz>> {
  }
  class EncryptedStream {
    +read(): String
  }
  class FileStream {
    +read(): String
  }
  abstract class StreamDecorator {
  }
}

StreamDecorator <|-- BufferedStream
StreamDecorator <|-- EncryptedStream
DataStream <|.. FileStream
DataStream <|.. StreamDecorator
Main ..> BufferedStream : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
